metadata.name: 春隣 -Harudonari-
metadata.description:
突如舞い降りた大きな変化に
私たちは戸惑う

期待か、それとも不安からか
心が揺れ動き、感情が湧き上がる
だからこそ
醜くも、美しくも感じるのだ

新しい春は、すぐそこまで来ている。

We are bewildered by the great change that has suddenly descended upon us.

Is it out of anticipation or anxiety?
Our hearts are shaken and our emotions well up.
That is why we feel both ugly and beautiful.

A new spring is just around the corner.
